 MERN Stack Chat App: A real-time chat application built with the MERN stack to provide seamless messaging functionality.

About The Project:
A real-time chat application built with the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, and Node.js) to provide seamless messaging functionality. This app includes features like user authentication, private messaging, and responsive design.

Built With:
Major frameworks/libraries used.
React
Express
shadcn
Tailwind
MongoDB
Socket.io

Prerequisites:
Ensure you have the following installed on your system: Node.js && MongoDB

Installation:
Clone the repo
Install NPM packages
RUN BACKEND
RUN FRONTEND

